<div class="jumbotron d-flex justify-content-center align-items-center" id="promotion">
  <div>
    <h1 class="text-center text-white">Coome</h1>
    <p class="text-center text-white app-description">make Cooking Menu Easier</p>
    <p class="text-center text-white app-description">今日は4人分だから...?<br>冷蔵庫の中に何が入ってたっけ?<br>何を買わなきゃいけないの?<br>そんな悩みがなくなるアプリです<br>
    <p class="text-center">
      <%= link_to  "試してみる", tops_index_path, class: "btn btn-success btn-lg mb-5", role: "button" %>
